node.text:
2 of our Beauty Ambassadors created their very OWN Liquid Matte Lipstick!! 

Soooo excited to finally reveal something that is so special to me and the team. In 2019, we collaborated with two of our amazing Beauty Ambassadors in the UK and brought them to Dubai to create their very own #LiquidMatte lipstick. Sana (from @theofficialselfridges) and Bilkis (from @harrodsbeauty) work their butts off to give people the products of their dreams, and we couldn't be more thankful for everything they do. My loves, it's been such an honor working with you both on creating your perfect shade and I'm sooooooo excited for the world to finally see them!!

💄'QUEEN OF SHEBA' by Bilkis (from @harrodsbeauty)– A royal pinky nude 💋

💄'GIRL ON FIRE' by Sana (from @theofficialselfridges) - A hot & toasted sexy red (what I’m currently wearing)💋 

I am OBSESSED with the shades they made & cant wait for you all to try them!! Officially dropped only on @harrodsbeauty & @theofficialselfridges

#GlazedBetterThanADoughnut
I love wearing this as a primer for a glowy base, as a highlighter on bare skin or on top of my makeup, there’s soooo much you can do with it. The formula legit melts into your skin in seconds but isn’t greasy or oily; it’s a highlighter-primer hybrid that gives this glass skin sheen, and smooths & blurs the appearance of fine lines & pores all at once.

Can’t wait to hear what you think my loves & please drop any questions you have below! Love you all so much
⠀⠀⠀⠀
*This video has not been retouched, smoothed or has any filters

node.text:
I've had ENOUGH with the mean comments online! You have NO idea what people might be going through and how hurtful a comment can be or how bad it can make someone feel. If you wouldn't feel comfortable saying it to someone’s face then you definitely shouldn't be commenting about it online either. If you have nothing kind to say, please just keep scrolling and say nothing at all! 

I honestly feel so grateful for the beautiful community we’ve built together, so please let’s remember to always put kindness first! Leaving a mean comment will never make you feel better!

Skin first, that glow-up second ✨ Here’s the low down of all those skin-loving ingredients in GloWish #LaunchingJune1
- Red Bell Pepper: packed full of Beta-Carotene, Vitamin C & A, and antioxidants. This superfood protects against blue light exposure (blue light speeds up your skin’s aging process!!)
- Damascus Rose Oil: my holy grail for fading acne scars and pigmentation. It also evens, soothe and locks-in extreme moisture
- Squalane: antioxidant that mimics our skin’s natural oils then controls it (making this perfect for dry to sensitive to oily skin types), it also helps lock in moisture and prevents fine lines

Some of you guys might be asking why it’s priced the way it is, because GloWish isn’t just makeup, it’s also a treatment packed with good-for-your-skin ingredients!! Also, it’s vegan, sustainable, not tested on animals and is derived from 90% natural ingredients!
